name: dart-mandelbrot
tagline: Mandelbrot experiments with Google's Dart Language
body:
### Mandelbrot Generator - A Dart (Lang) Experiment

This port of a Mandelbrot generator to Dart was created during a Google Hack-a-Thon in Freemont (Seattle), WA on July 14, 2012.

by Mike Koss (@mckoss), Bobby Seidensticker (@bobby-seidensticker), and Brandon Donnelson (@branflake2267).

This code is released under a Creative Commons Attribution license by the authors.
